data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUN 1/14/24 between 2:00 - 4:00 pm * Great Price & Perfect Location to EVERYTHING!!! Gorgeous 3br 2.5ba 2 Story Home * Open Floorplan with Kitchen open to Breakfast Room & Greatroom, but also enjoy the Separate Dining Room * Laundry Room on the main level with 1/2 bath * You won't be disappointed with the brand NEW high-end kitchen with soft close doors and drawers & floating shelves * All NEW flooring; Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) throughout main level, all NEW carpet, and NEW bathroom flooring * Interior has New Paint * Owners Suite is LARGE with a very generous sitting area, New Tub and Walk-In Closet * Oversized secondary bedroom * Lakeshore Community offers sidewalks, street lights, swimming pool, tennis courts, and playground * Minutes to Ashley Park, Downtown Newnan, Piedmont Hospital, City of Hope (Cancer Centers of America), and minutes to I-85 * Come make this your new home!
